      • TaskTO

        public TaskTO(Task task,
              boolean skipHandlerCreation)
       throws ClassNotFoundException,
              InstantiationException,
              IllegalAccessException
        Creates this TaskTO out of the given Task entity.
        Parameters:
        task - The task.
        skipHandlerCreation - If true, the handler wouldn't be created through the constructor.
        Throws:
        ClassNotFoundException - Thrown, if there is no class for the given handler.
        IllegalAccessException - Thrown, if it was not possible to initialize the handler class.
        InstantiationException - Thrown, if it was not possible to initialize the handler class.
